projects.name: Plant Disease Diagnosis
projects.description: Plant Disease Diagnosis is done using CNN deep learning model for image recognition and developed a web application to make it available for everyone and used flask framework. The aim of this project is to create an automated system that leverages computer vision techniques to recognise plant diseases from photographs taken using mobile or other devices.

projects.name: Airline Reservation in java
projects.description: Designed a comprehensive GUI application for airplane reservations using Java, featuring numerous functionalities. The system is integrated with an SQL database for backend support.
